<% content_for :exhibition do %>
  <div class="articleContainer">
    <div class="spacer">
      <div class="description">
        <article>
          <div class="column">
<h1>What is <%= image_tag 'projectlodge-light.png', :alt => '.projectlodge',:class => 'projectlodgeLogo' %>?</h1>
            <p>The question should not be what, but who! Linking people together in an open and free environment to do what they like to do.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <p> Create musical instruments, collaborate on art pieces, helping out a local causes, plan performances and anything you can imagine. Innovating together in technology and growing personally in knowledge.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <p>We as .projectlodge ARE the platform on wich we do innovative, technological and fun projects. Together on Local and Global level. We find each other and collaborate on the future!</p>
            <p style="display:none">We want to enable the individual to contribute to the world on their own terms, level and field.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="break"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
